  "detailed_description": "Everyone is born with an appearance of some sort, but you simply don't seem to know what you are...<br>Raybound is a short adventure where you are a textureless square that must go on a quest to find yourself...<br><br>- Cast your rays on objects to navigate the world, with these strange, synthetic flowers...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626370/extras/40582a89c8a990052d64adb67d85b3f3.poster.avif?t=1756477612\" width=572 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626370/extras/40582a89c8a990052d64adb67d85b3f3.webm?t=1756477612\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626370/extras/40582a89c8a990052d64adb67d85b3f3.mp4?t=1756477612\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>- Go through five chapters that test your skill in puzzle solving and platforming. Are these, stars?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626370/extras/c2132748b2aa303f8a920e2c7ed1cee2.avif?t=1756477612\" width=572 height=194 /></span><br><br>- Experience bizarre scenarios that may lead you into a reality beyond ours...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626370/extras/c6881f447d78669f4c3e8352ab2b0791.avif?t=1756477612\" width=572 height=194 /></span><br><br>- And you get to look at this pricket having a good sleep...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1626370/extras/b7cba868ec25f92619c9f1bef7bbefe9.poster.avif?t=1756477612\" width=572 height=194 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st